Backend Setup

Prerequisites
- Node.js (LTS recommended)
- npm

Setup Files (IMPORTANT)
Before running the backend, copy all files from the setup folder into the backend folder.

From:
backend/setup/

To:
backend/

After copying the files, the setup folder can be ignored or deleted.

Install Dependencies
The node_modules folder is NOT included in this repository.

Run the following commands:
cd backend
npm install

This will install all required dependencies.

Run Backend
Start the backend server:
npm start

Or:
npm run dev

Notes
- Always copy the setup files before running npm install
- Do not push node_modules to GitHub
